export function t(key: TranslationKey, lang: Language = 'en'): string {
  const keys = key.split('.');
  let value: any = translations[lang];
  
  for (const k of keys) {
    if (value && value[k]) {
      value = value[k];
    } else {
      return key; // Fallback to the key if translation not found
    }
  }
  
  return value;
}
